OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,6,Fday with some sunny spells. Showers
OL,7,Fwill develop for the afternoon, some
OL,8,Fof which may be heavy and thundery.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FShowers will clear away this
OL,11,Fevening. Then dry with clear spells in
OL,12,Fthe west, while eastern areas will see
OL,13,Frather murky conditions with a risk of
OL,14,Fmist, fog and drizzle.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FMainly dry and settled with
OL,17,Flight winds. Cloudy at first with damp
OL,18,Fand murky conditions for eastern
OL,19,Fcoasts, but soon brightening up with
OL,20,Fsome good spells of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
