OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled conditions through the
OL,7,Fperiod, with plenty of sunshine for
OL,8,Fmost. Some patchy cloud may linger
OL,9,Faround eastern coasts at times in the
OL,10,Fmornings.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
